# internal-data

# Description

Private properties implementation using WeakMap as described on [MDN - Private Properties](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/Add-ons/SDK/Guides/Contributor_s_Guide/Private_Properties).

# Synopsis

## Flow

```js
